				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10525806/scp-3763#post-4175286</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2019 16:07:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Generic_Viking</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4873703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I second this opinion. The letters are touching, but they don't add anything. The main article already hints at a man with a dead father, whose car he inherited, and a missing or dead mother.</p> <p>But, I upvoted the SCP anyways.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10525806#post-4174889</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10525806/scp-3763#post-4174889</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2019 08:58:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MaliceAforethought</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I believe it's Euclid because there's a living human who is a component of the anomaly. They need to be contained too, and <em>that</em> requires more than the basic &quot;box it up and stick it in a warehouse&quot; procedure.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10525806#post-4174876</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10525806/scp-3763#post-4174876</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2019 08:38:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Damian Uck</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4034441</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Why is this Euclid?<br /> Other than the &quot;keep people away&quot; effect, can't you just box this up in a slightly larger than usual containment cell?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10525806#post-4174590</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10525806/scp-3763#post-4174590</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2019 02:21:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>thewalkindude</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902115</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Not sure how I feel about the letters at the end. It feels like you're working too hard to add a story to a piece that really doesn't need one. It would be stronger without them. It bothers me, but not enough to downvote or no vote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
